Browser Feature Coverage

This page will be automatically built every week showing the status of supported browser feature.

The data is generated using json file retreived by running latest Servo commit through a local instance of mdn-bcd-collector which performs browser feature detection. Then relevant links of specs will be retrieved through mdn‚Äôs browser-compat-data.
